{"data": [{"id": "4742515", "title": "Capital Southwest: Buying The Dip Despite Dividend Risks", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2045262949/image_2045262949.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Excited Businessman Raises Hands and Punches Air while Celebrating Successful Deal. Stock Exchange Manager Happy After Investment Day. Broker in White Shirt Wins a Profitable Contract. Back View\" data-id=\"2045262949\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"810px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2045262949/image_2045262949.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2045262949/image_2045262949.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2045262949/image_2045262949.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2045262949/image_2045262949.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2045262949/image_2045262949.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2045262949/image_2045262949.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2045262949/image_2045262949.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2045262949/image_2045262949.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">gorodenkoff</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Capital Southwest (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CSWC\" title=\"Capital Southwest\">CSWC</a></span>) has provided investors with quite a lot of volatility over the last six months, when its stock price has decreased by over 10%. Lower valuation combined with an attractive dividend yield leaves investors wondering whether the recent</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2045262949/image_2045262949.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742515-capital-southwest-stock-buying-dip-despite-dividend-risks", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 06:59:04"}, {"id": "4742514", "title": "IWF May Struggle To Sustain Its Robust Return In 2025, But IWD Could Shine", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173998931/image_2173998931.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Year 2025 business concept. Economic and financial analysis, interest rates, stocks, bonds, ranking, mortgage, loan rates, Percent, up or down, arrow symbol, copy space. navy blue background\" data-id=\"2173998931\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173998931/image_2173998931.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173998931/image_2173998931.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173998931/image_2173998931.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173998931/image_2173998931.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173998931/image_2173998931.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173998931/image_2173998931.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173998931/image_2173998931.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173998931/image_2173998931.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Andrzej Rostek</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The solid tech earnings, rate cuts and economic growth continue to offer a cushion against lofty valuation, helping iShares Russell 1000 Growth ETF (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/IWF\" title=\"iShares Russell 1000 Growth ETF\">IWF</a></span>) soar to its all-time high. Although these factors are likely to favour the stock</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173998931/image_2173998931.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742514-iwf-may-struggle-sustain-robust-return-2025-but-iwd-could-shine", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 06:50:15"}, {"id": "4742512", "title": "SPYI: A 12% Yield With A Nice Tax Treatment", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1809155192/image_1809155192.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Two executive businessperson colleagues consultation\" data-id=\"1809155192\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1809155192/image_1809155192.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1809155192/image_1809155192.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1809155192/image_1809155192.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1809155192/image_1809155192.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1809155192/image_1809155192.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1809