.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106056\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742516-samsara-inc-2025-q3-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 05:59:23"}, {"id": "4742506", "title": "Infrastructure Outlook: Bridging The Valuation Gap", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/931745268/image_931745268.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Electricity pylons at sunset\" data-id=\"931745268\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/931745268/image_931745268.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/931745268/image_931745268.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/931745268/image_931745268.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/931745268/image_931745268.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/931745268/image_931745268.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/931745268/image_931745268.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/931745268/image_931745268.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/931745268/image_931745268.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">James O'Neil</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Defensive and Diversifying Returns Valuable in 2025</h2> <p>The concentrated market of 2024 and the return of inflationary pressures are a good reminder of what sets infrastructure apart from other asset classes and why this will be valuable in</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/931745268/image_931745268.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742506-infrastructure-outlook-bridging-the-valuation-gap", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 05:45:00"}, {"id": "4742500", "title": "EEM: This Is Why Emerging Markets Are Promising", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733709478/image_1733709478.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"banknotes of the BRICS states\" data-id=\"1733709478\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733709478/image_1733709478.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733709478/image_1733709478.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733709478/image_1733709478.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733709478/image_1733709478.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733709478/image_1733709478.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733709478/image_1733709478.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733709478/image_1733709478.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733709478/image_1733709478.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Bjoern Wylezich</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>I recommend buying the iShares MSCI Emerging Markets ETF (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/EEM\" title=\"iShares MSCI Emerging Markets ETF\">EEM</a></span>). The U.S. has outperformed the global market for the past 15 years, and the S&amp;P 500 (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SPX\" title=\"S&amp;P 500 Index\">SPX</a>) is on track to return over</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733709478/image_1733709478.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742500-eemetf-emerging-markets-promising", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 05:21:17"}, {"id": "4742494", "title": "Amplify Energy: Encouraging Continued Results From Beta Development", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1265591214/image_1265591214.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"High angle view of an oil rig close to shore, Cromarty Firth, Scotland, United Kingdom\" data-id=\"1265591214\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1023px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1265591214/image_1265591214.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1265591214/image_1265591214.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1265591214/image_1265591214.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1265591214/image_1265591214.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1265591214/image_1265591214.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1265591214/image_1265591214.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1265591214/image_1265591214.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1265591214/image_1265591214.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Abstract Aerial Art</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Amplify Energy (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AMPY\" title=\"Amplify Energy Corp.\">AMPY</a></span>) continues to <a href=\"https://www.amplifyenergy.com/investor-relations/press-releases/press-release-details/2024/Amplify-Energy-Announces-Third-Quarter-2024-Results-Beta-Drilling-Results-and-Issuance-of-Sustainability-Report/default.aspx\" rel=\"noopener noopener noopener noopener\">report strong results</a> from its new Beta wells. Both its A50 and C59 wells have performed above expectations to date, and it has two more wells to report from its 2024 Beta</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1265591214/image_1265591214.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742494-amplify-energy-ampy-stock-encouraging-results-from-beta-development", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 05:10:00"}, {"id": "4742489", "title": "KCE: A Pre- And Post-Election Winner, Shares Extended (Rating Downgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/114854593/image_114854593.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Customer signing paperwork with bank manager\" data-id=\"114854593\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/114854593/image_114854593.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/114854593/image_114854593.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/up